    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! We're talking no scratches, no dents, and an interior that still has that fresh car smell. It drives like a total dream and is just waiting for someone to take it on a new adventure. Come take a look\u2014you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
