    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this motorcar\u2014from its unblemished exterior finish to its pristine, smoke-free interior\u2014has been maintained to the most exacting standards. Mechanically superior and cosmetically flawless, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unparalleled caliber, suited for the most discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
