    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to check out this absolute beauty. It is in seriously incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, kept it garaged, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and is just waiting for someone to take it on a new adventure. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
