    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents a masterclass in mechanical harmony. Under the hood, the S54B32 inline-six features individual throttle bodies and double VANOS, delivering a high-revving, linear power curve with zero hesitation. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. This chassis is exceptionally clean, with proactive rear subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout to maintain structural integrity. Every component, from the Sachs dampers to the cross-drilled rotors, remains in peak operational state, ensuring the iconic M-Division handling remains uncompromised.",
